```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Voyager
    participant Curriculum as CurriculumAgent
    participant Action as ActionAgent
    participant Skill as SkillManager
    participant Critic as CriticAgent
    participant Env as VoyagerEnv
    participant Mineflayer as Mineflayer Server

    Note over User,Mineflayer: INITIALIZATION PHASE
    User->>Voyager: voyager.learn()
    Voyager->>Env: env.reset(mode="hard", wait_ticks=40)
    Env->>Mineflayer: POST /start {host, port, reset, inventory, equipment, waitTicks}
    Mineflayer-->>Env: return events (JSON)
    Env-->>Voyager: return events
    Voyager->>Voyager: last_events = env.step("")

    Note over User,Mineflayer: LEARNING LOOP BEGINS
    loop Until max_iterations reached
        Note over Curriculum,Mineflayer: TASK PROPOSAL PHASE
        Voyager->>Curriculum: propose_next_task(events, chest_observation)
        Curriculum->>Curriculum: render_observation(events)
        Curriculum->>Curriculum: run_qa(events) [if progress >= warm_up["context"]]
        Curriculum->>Curriculum: render_human_message(events)
        Curriculum->>Curriculum: llm.invoke([system_msg, human_msg])
        Note right of Curriculum: GPT-4 proposes next task<br/>based on current state
        Curriculum-->>Voyager: return (task, context)

        Note over Voyager,Mineflayer: TASK EXECUTION PHASE (ROLLOUT)
        Voyager->>Voyager: rollout(task, context)
        Voyager->>Voyager: reset(task, context, reset_env=True)
        Voyager->>Env: env.reset(mode="soft")
        Env->>Mineflayer: POST /start {host, port, reset="soft", ...}
        Mineflayer-->>Env: return events
        Voyager->>Env: env.step("/time set ...; /difficulty peaceful;")
        Env->>Mineflayer: POST /step {code, programs}
        Note right of Mineflayer: Execute JS code:<br/>bot.chat("/time set ...")
        Mineflayer-->>Env: return events (observation)
        Env-->>Voyager: return events

        Note over Skill,Voyager: SKILL RETRIEVAL
        Voyager->>Skill: retrieve_skills(context)
        Skill->>Skill: vectordb.similarity_search_with_score(query, k=5)
        Note right of Skill: Searches ChromaDB for<br/>relevant skills using<br/>OpenAI embeddings
        Skill-->>Voyager: return [skill_code_1, skill_code_2, ...]

        Note over Action,Voyager: ACTION AGENT INITIALIZATION
        Voyager->>Action: render_system_message(skills)
        Action-->>Voyager: return SystemMessage(programs + response_format)
        Voyager->>Action: render_human_message(events, code, task, context, critique)
        Action-->>Voyager: return HumanMessage(observation + task + context)
        Voyager->>Voyager: messages = [system_message, human_message]

        Note over Voyager,Mineflayer: ITERATIVE PROMPTING LOOP
        loop Until success OR max_retries (4)
            Note over Action,Voyager: CODE GENERATION
            Voyager->>Action: llm.invoke(messages)
            Note right of Action: GPT-4 generates<br/>JavaScript code to<br/>accomplish task
            Action-->>Voyager: return AIMessage(js_code)
            Voyager->>Action: process_ai_message(ai_message)
            Note right of Action: Parse JS code using Babel:<br/>- Extract functions<br/>- Find main async function<br/>- Validate structure
            Action-->>Voyager: return {program_code, program_name, exec_code}

            Note over Env,Mineflayer: CODE EXECUTION
            Voyager->>Voyager: code = program_code + exec_code
            Voyager->>Env: env.step(code, programs)
            Note right of Voyager: code: Generated JS function<br/>programs: All skill functions + primitives
            Env->>Env: requests.post(server/step, {code, programs})
            Env->>Mineflayer: POST /step {code, programs}
            Note right of Mineflayer: Server receives payload:<br/>{<br/>  code: "await funcName(bot);",<br/>  programs: "all skill functions..."<br/>}

            Note over Mineflayer: MINEFLAYER EXECUTION
            Mineflayer->>Mineflayer: eval("(async () => {" + programs + code + "})()")
            Note right of Mineflayer: 1. Load all skill functions<br/>2. Execute main code<br/>3. Bot interacts with Minecraft<br/>4. Collect observations
            Mineflayer->>Mineflayer: bot.observe()
            Note right of Mineflayer: Gather events:<br/>- onChat messages<br/>- onError messages<br/>- observe (final state)
            Mineflayer-->>Env: return events [{event_type, event_data}, ...]

            Note over Env: RESPONSE HANDLING
            Env->>Env: Handle encoding: decode UTF-8, parse JSON
            Env-->>Voyager: return events
            Voyager->>Voyager: recorder.record(events, task)
            Voyager->>Action: update_chest_memory(nearbyChests)

            Note over Critic,Voyager: TASK VERIFICATION
            Voyager->>Critic: check_task_success(events, task, context, chest_observation)
            Critic->>Critic: render_human_message(events, task, context)
            Note right of Critic: Check for errors in events
            Critic->>Critic: llm.invoke([system_msg, human_msg])
            Note right of Critic: GPT-4 evaluates if<br/>task was successful
            Critic-->>Voyager: return (success, critique)

            alt If reset_placed_if_failed AND not success
                Note over Voyager,Mineflayer: REVERT PLACED BLOCKS
                Voyager->>Voyager: Extract placed blocks from events
                Voyager->>Env: env.step(givePlacedItemBack(...), programs)
                Env->>Mineflayer: POST /step
                Mineflayer-->>Env: return updated events
                Voyager->>Voyager: Update events with reverted state
            end

            Note over Action,Skill: CONTEXT UPDATE FOR NEXT ITERATION
            Voyager->>Skill: retrieve_skills(context + chatlog)
            Skill-->>Voyager: return new_skills
            Voyager->>Action: render_system_message(new_skills)
            Voyager->>Action: render_human_message(events, code, task, context, critique)
            Action-->>Voyager: return new messages
            Voyager->>Voyager: messages = [system_message, human_message]

            alt If success
                break Exit retry loop
            end
        end

        Note over Skill,Voyager: SKILL LEARNING
        alt If task succeeded
            Voyager->>Skill: add_new_skill(info)
            Note right of Skill: info contains:<br/>- task<br/>- program_code<br/>- program_name
            Skill->>Skill: generate_skill_description(program_name, program_code)
            Note right of Skill: Use GPT to generate<br/>description of skill
            Skill->>Skill: vectordb.add_texts([description], ids=[name])
            Note right of Skill: Add to ChromaDB for<br/>future retrieval
            Skill->>Skill: Save to disk: code, description, skills.json
        end

        Note over Curriculum,Voyager: CURRICULUM UPDATE
        Voyager->>Curriculum: update_exploration_progress(info)
        alt If success
            Curriculum->>Curriculum: completed_tasks.append(task)
        else If failed
            Curriculum->>Curriculum: failed_tasks.append(task)
        end
        Curriculum->>Curriculum: clean_up_tasks()
        Curriculum->>Curriculum: Save to disk: completed_tasks.json, failed_tasks.json
    end

    Note over User,Mineflayer: LEARNING COMPLETE
    Voyager-->>User: return {completed_tasks, failed_tasks, skills}
```